                                <support>
                                    <p><material>Rock</material>-cut <objectType>tomb</objectType> with one door giving access to the chamber; on the front wall false masonry
                                        is designed and the door frame forms a large lintel with a moulding above, into which five small niches were cut off later, along with three others on the 
                                        facade; above again there is a Doric built entablature
                                         (dimensions not registered).</p>
